examples.en: I think he has been seasoning his story with a few inventions.
The stories he told about his military service were just inventions.
The light bulb was one of the most important inventions of the 19th century.
Nobel left the world two inventions - dynamite and his eponymous peace price.
The Franklin stove, bifocals, and the lightning rod are just a few of the inventions that we owe to the fecund creativity of Benjamin Franklin.
